<subSubSection pageId="821" pageNumber="822" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="821" pageNumber="822">
<pageBreakToken pageId="821" pageNumber="822" start="start">Distribution</pageBreakToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="821" pageNumber="822">The range of this species extends from southwestern Maine (Majka et al. 2011: 47) and southwestern Quebec (LeSage 1996: 22) to southeastern South Dakota (Kirk and Balsbaugh 1975: 37), including southernmost Ontario (Pettit 1869: 107; CNC), south to southeastern Texas along the Rio Grande and southern Florida [see Madge 1967: Fig. 122]. The record from &quot;North Dakota&quot; (Bousquet and Larochelle 1993: 278) needs confirmation.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
